data.description: Feel like you are on vacation year round in this beautiful log home on 5 plus acres fully fenced and cross fenced perfect for your hobby farm. The moment you walk in the door you feel like you are miles away. Main floor hosts living, dining room along with Kitchen one bedroom and full bath.  Upstairs greats you with a large loft area along with primary bedroom and three quarter bath. Enjoy nature from the balcony of the primary bedroom. Large shop with lift is perfect for all your projects.
